  "title": "Do you like to yap? ✨ 🗣️",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>At Royal Org, we believe the people make a difference. Like clay in a potter’s hand, we continuously mould each individual by giving them room to make mistakes, opportunities to be exposed to, and grow as a family. We strongly believe in guiding, leading and walking together as a team to achieve success.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>🌸 Join the Vibe — Become an Sales & Marketing Ambassador! 🌸 Represent major brands at events and campaigns by engaging with people authentically, creating memorable experiences, and driving campaign success.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Engage attendees at brand events and campaigns to build genuine connections and promote brand awareness</li><li>Deliver energetic and authentic brand representation to create positive impressions and buzz</li><li>Achieve and exceed event goals by actively interacting with the public and encouraging participation</li><li>Collaborate with team members to ensure smooth event execution and a fun, supportive atmosphere</li><li>Adapt communication style to connect with diverse audiences and enhance brand experiences</li><li>Learn and apply training to improve event performance and personal growth continuously</li></ul>",
